{ This drill is fairly popular, so I wouldn't doubt if you've come across it. Mark all of the squares that the queen's have in common. For example: Both queen's might move to the f4 square on this turn - so f4 would get a mark. } { [%csl Gf4,Gc6,Gd4,Gc3,Ge6,Gf7] }
