{ Go as deep as possible into each opening sequence. After each move - ask yourself which pieces are still invisible for both sides. Write down your moves so you can play them back with a full chess set to check your answers. Students often play pieces through pawns and make other illegal moves in the first few attempts at this drill. }
 *


